  "detailed_description": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/697910/extras/3139d0951f1c2f6da2d6846aae32ddda.avif?t=1512112829\" width=521 height=108 /></span><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/697910/extras/d2fbf0c685651c40313ea7ce4acf770b.poster.avif?t=1512112829\" width=640 height=168 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/697910/extras/d2fbf0c685651c40313ea7ce4acf770b.webm?t=1512112829\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/697910/extras/d2fbf0c685651c40313ea7ce4acf770b.mp4?t=1512112829\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>Temple Raid VR is a classic exploration game developed specifically for VR. The call of a timeless guardian draws you into an ancient temple, where you can discover a great treasure that has been undisturbed for eons! Navigate the perils of the temple using VR motion controllers. Climb around and explore inside this mysterious world, and solve the puzzles that guard the treasure.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/697910/extras/543180edcc027f23fc852bdab7f65a60.webp?t=1512112829\" width=359 height=39 /></span><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/697910/extras/4e96c7812177554d83dd0e25549981f7.poster.avif?t=1512112829\" width=640 height=202 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/697910/extras/4e96c7812177554d83dd0e25549981f7.webm?t=1512112829\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/697910/extras/4e96c7812177554d83dd0e25549981f7.mp4?t=1512112829\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>Think Tomb Raider: climb and problem-solve your way through the temple in VR in order to reveal the treasure that lies within. While the premise seems simple enough, the treasure has been sitting there for 10,000 years, and it won't be an easy feat to acquire it. An ominous guardian with an ancient, raspy voice protects this temple. The guardian isn't too keen to see you.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/697910/extras/64561884538eb79c0784f5c0f966e0f6.webp?t=1512112829\" width=119 height=38 /></span><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/697910/extras/7626ab5351ad902830d454d070402d93.poster.avif?t=1512112829\" width=640 height=190 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/697910/extras/7626ab5351ad902830d454d070402d93.webm?t=1512112829\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/697910/extras/7626ab5351ad902830d454d070402d93.mp4?t=1512112829\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>Realistic climbing along treacherous cliffs and fling yourself across ravines!<br></li><li>Single Player Campaign split into manageable scenes and bite-sized checkpoints<br></li><li>Collect Gems and Idols are strewn around this forgotten ruin<br></li><li>Built exclusively to take advantage of VR and motion controllers</li></ul>",
  "about_the_game": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/697910/extras/3139d0951f1c2f6da2d6846aae32ddda.avif?t=1512112829\" width=521 height=108 /></span><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/697910/extras/d2fbf0c685651c40313ea7ce4acf770b.poster.avif?t=1512112829\" width=640 height=168 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/697910/extras/d2fbf0c685651c40313ea7ce4acf770b.webm?t=1512112829\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/697910/extras/d2fbf0c685651c40313ea7ce4acf770b.mp4?t=1512112829\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>Temple Raid VR is a classic exploration game developed specifically for VR. The call of a timeless guardian draws you into an ancient temple, where you can discover a great treasure that has been undisturbed for eons! Navigate the perils of the temple using VR motion controllers. Climb around and explore inside this mysterious world, and solve the puzzles that guard the treasure.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/697910/extras/543180edcc027f23fc852bdab7f65a60.webp?t=1512112829\" width=359 height=39 /></span><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/697910/extras/4e96c7812177554d83dd0e25549981f7.poster.avif?t=1512112829\" width=640 height=202 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/697910/extras/4e96c7812177554d83dd0e25549981f7.webm?t=1512112829\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/697910/extras/4e96c7812177554d83dd0e25549981f7.mp4?t=1512112829\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>Think Tomb Raider: climb and problem-solve your way through the temple in VR in order to reveal the treasure that lies within. While the premise seems simple enough, the treasure has been sitting there for 10,000 years, and it won't be an easy feat to acquire it. An ominous guardian with an ancient, raspy voice protects this temple. The guardian isn't too keen to see you.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/697910/extras/64561884538eb79c0784f5c0f966e0f6.webp?t=1512112829\" width=119 height=38 /></span><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/697910/extras/7626ab5351ad902830d454d070402d93.poster.avif?t=1512112829\" width=640 height=190 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/697910/extras/7626ab5351ad902830d454d070402d93.webm?t=1512112829\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/697910/extras/7626ab5351ad902830d454d070402d93.mp4?t=1512112829\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>Realistic climbing along treacherous cliffs and fling yourself across ravines!<br></li><li>Single Player Campaign split into manageable scenes and bite-sized checkpoints<br></li><li>Collect Gems and Idols are strewn around this forgotten ruin<br></li><li>Built exclusively to take advantage of VR and motion controllers</li></ul>",
